item.title: Terminal Setup
item.description: This guide will walk you through how I setup my terminal in macOs. The terminal is an integral part of my workflow and I have a list of tools that I have been using for years. And since setting up my environment usually only happens once on a new machine, there are times where I forget how to set it up so this will serve as a reference for myself as well.
